Object Picker

 

The Object picker allows you to perform basic or advanced search in the system and to select (pick) one or more objects from the search for further manipulations.

The object picker does not exist independently, it is extension to other important system functionalities like widgets, in which searches are performed.

Object Picker Header

 

At the top of the picker is displayed the action that is executed. It can be Widget configuration as shown, or Add thumbnail or Move to ect.

Basic search in object picker

 

The object picker functionality allows you to perform basic search for objects in the system and select (pick) one or more objects from the search result for further manipulations.

 

Note: For more information look

Advance search in the object picker

 

In the object picker you are able to perform advance search for objects in the system and select (pick) one or more objects from the search result for further manipulations.

Note: For more information look

Basket Tab

 

All the object selected via searches are moved to the basket tab. In this tab you can see the selected object and deselect some if needed.

Tab Recently used in the Object Picker

 

In the object picker you are able to select an object you have recently used, instead to search for it.
